This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and textual coherence. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves analyzing and categorizing news articles. Additionally, the use of data-driven analytics suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the societal significance of fake news could place it in the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-category.
